column5: I know I have not been around for a while ... buttttt I just wanted to Wish all my friends that I have not spoke with for a while MERRY CHRISTMAS TO ALL  and a safe one to boot
Right back at ya bud!  Hope you have a great time over the holiday season.  Cheers!

Merry Christmas to you too Kelvin and all the best in the New Year.

Merry Xmas to you too Kelvin.

Same to you Kelvin and a very good New Year.
